      *      DBIO-KEY입력없으면SKIP
      *     차주번호／차주번호구분／통합계정과목코드
             IF  IN-BRWR-NO          =  SPACE  OR
                 IN-BRWR-NO-DSTCD    =  SPACE  OR
                 IN-CARD-LNBZ-IDNFR  =  SPACE  OR
                 IN-INTGRA-TIACC-CD  =  SPACE
             THEN
                 ADD   CO-NUM-1    TO  WK-AC-SKIP-CNT
             ELSE
                  PERFORM  S3400-KJL0022-INSERT-RTN
                     THRU  S3400-KJL0022-INSERT-EXT
             END-IF

